      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"f95f3502-b390-43df-b755-6ad7b1b7efe1\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Rendering</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/567017582/FC_AOVs.mov?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762976102072&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760\">FC_AOVs.mov</a></span><p>When it came time to render the final image in XPU, I used a variety of passes, including LPES, AOVS, and separate fog layers for both the leading UFO light and the headlights.</p><p>The video above breaks down these passes.</p><p /><p /><div class=\"panel conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"a1d08b94-349f-4eb9-9426-5b2261fb2851\" data-macro-name=\"panel\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;border-width: 1px;\"><div class=\"panelContent\" style=\"background-color: #4C9AFF;\">\n<p><strong><span class=\"legacy-color-text-inverse\">Compositing</span></strong></p>\n</div></div><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><a href=\"/wiki/download/attachments/567017582/FC_Layers.mov?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762678179568&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760\">FC_Layers.mov</a></span><p>The video above demonstrates how those AOVS and LPES were recomposited, refined, and the final image finalized.</p><p>Of course, there’s always a load of ways you can develop the look of the final render in comp, so here are a few other fun looks I experimented with.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"AltOption1.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567017582/AltOption1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680315028&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=409\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567017582/AltOption1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680315028&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1069\" data-width=\"1982\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"657424951\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"AltOption1.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"567017582\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"11\" data-media-id=\"0226e003-0d38-4723-a030-b0bee496e8de\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567017582/AltOption1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680315028&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=818 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567017582/AltOption1.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680315028&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=409 1x\"></span><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"AltOption2.png\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/567017582/AltOption2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680339121&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=408\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/567017582/AltOption2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1762680339121&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1069\" data-width=\"1987\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=